\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n民建聯多名成員今早與特首林鄭月娥會面，包括主席李慧琼、立法會議員柯創盛、鄭泳舜等。民建聯建議政府牽頭成立︱止暴協調中心」，讓全港市民參與制止暴力的行動，在安全的情況下協助清理路障及連儂牆，增加市民社區參與；</span></span>又要求政府增加人手和增聘警力舒緩警方壓力，例如在經常有暴亂出現的位置安排警員站崗，主動預防暴亂發生，以及由相關政府部門即時發放準備的交通資訊，協助市民出門。 <br />\n<br />\n李慧琼表示，暴力不斷升級，若只得警隊在前線執勤，其他官員和市民無法參與或政府沒有推出具協調的聯合行動，情況只會持續惡化。她又說，普遍市民都不想見到暴力繼續升級下去，認為大家是時候冷靜下來「慢慢傾」，之後政府就可以進行改革，回應市民訴求及其他深層次矛盾。"},{"pid":"3b6c7b44b4024037114cc064a85df516185ba3f1","tid":1719510,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c144293220fcd4b81d107e1f99e4c2fd85a1a32","tid":1719510,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e510b8946eddbde7461b2564fb919d762fa13d","tid":1719510,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:18:27.000Z","msg":"冷靜左之後睬你都傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59974fd06f07c147fe0edaaa187d18d08a0b73c2","tid":1719510,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}